				        		<label>입사년월 : <input id="workStartDate" type="month" max="2040-12" min="1920-12" value="2024-03"></label>
				        		<label>퇴사년월 : <input id="workEndDate" type="month" max="2040-12" min="1920-12" value="2025-03"></label>
				        	</span>
				        </h3>
